data.description: ***Multiple Offers*** Price Reduced! Seller to contribute $5k toward a temporary buy-down rate of a 1% reduction! VA Buyers! Assumable VA Loan. Seller wants to retain his VA Benefit. Contact me for a possible 2nd Mortgage for the difference. Move-in ready! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and sophistication in this spacious 2-story single-family home in the heart of Bluffdale. Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, the fully finished basement is a retreat. Unwind in the hot tub under the charming gazebo, or entertain in style with CAT6A Audio wiring for 5.1 in the main floor great room. The basement offers peace and privacy with sound and fire insulation in the walls and ceiling. Practical upgrades abound including granite counters, stainless steel appliances, central vacuum, security camera, a laundry room pedestal, epoxy floors in the garage, and side-mount garage door openers. Enjoy modern living with ceiling fans in all bedrooms, office, and family rooms, plus 30-year memory foam carpet pad. Hot Tub & TV are included. Refrigerator, Washer & Dryer are negotiable. Buyer needs to have VA benefit to be able to Fully Assume VA Loan 2.25% int rate, $2,092.85 payment, $413,864 Loan Balance. Schedule a showing today!
